Vladimir Igorovich Arnol'd is a Russian mathematician and mathematical physicist; working in Moscow and Paris. 

* wikipedia: [English](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vladimir_Arnold), [French]()

* biography at MacTutor [history of math archive](http://www-history.mcs.st-andrews.ac.uk/Biographies/Arnold.html)

